info.name: SOAP: MailSender
info.description:
An example of using Postman for your [SOAP requests](http://blog.getpostman.com/2017/11/18/postman-makes-soap-requests-too/).

> A newer example of [using Postman for SOAP](https://blog.postman.com/making-http-soap-requests-with-postman/).

body.raw:
<soapenv:Envelope xmlns:soapenv="http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/soap/envelope/" xmlns:ps="http://pismo">
 <soapenv:Body>
    <ps:pismo tipPriloga="pdf">
  <ps:primalac>igi.l.1999@gmail.com</ps:primalac>
  <ps:naslov>Odobrenje zahteva</ps:naslov>
  <ps:sadrzaj>Vas zahtev je odobren</ps:sadrzaj>
  <ps:prilog>
  
  </ps:prilog>
</ps:pismo>
 </soapenv:Body>
</soapenv:Envelope>

request.description: This example uses a holiday web service to query which holidays occur in the month of November.
